{"tid":537070,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"下星期去東京行程請教","createTime":"2018-01-22T11:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T07:11:56.000Z","uid":21225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"47a8a03bbc898c1b6f30eeb961cd49860c1be18a","tid":537070,"uid":21225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T11:12:47.000Z","msg":"不是伸手黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n星期六凌晨機飛東京 好多想去嘅都唔開<br />\n好難搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n*對購物無咩興趣 住池袋<br />\n<br />\n星期六：淺草（雷門、淺草寺、合羽橋道具街、曹源寺），行去skytree，池袋<br />\n（午餐：並木藪蕎麦 晚餐：無敵家）<br />\n<br />\n星期日：明治神宮、代代木公園市集、渋谷、表參道、Tokyo City View and Sky Deck、東京鐵塔<br />\n（早餐：Bills Pancake）<br />\n<br />\n星期一：築地市場、東京車站、大宮、川越<br />\n（早餐：磯壽司 午餐：大宮いずみや食堂 晚餐：久利牛舌）<br />\n<br />\n星期二：荒川線、神保町<br />\n<br />\n星期三：淺草、上野<br />\n（早餐：淺草宿六飯糰 午餐：鰻禪）<br />\n<br />\n仲有無咩野食係新宿，涉谷，表參道個邊推介同埋去<br />\n<br />\n第一次去東京好難plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119c0edb383c7fe8b2a5c94a8a5ca54e60f429e4","tid":537070,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T11:49:13.000Z","msg":"睇定天氣預報吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484d339602a1862cbbfa847a40f2d687f7f2adc0","tid":537070,"uid":12690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T11:51:22.000Z","msg":"剛係東京返黎 ，skytree唔抵去 入場先比2千幾yen 上到塔頂 再要比多千幾yen <br />\n不過佢地家陣有擺緊超時空要塞<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/22/195105_48c2a33b357ba91c701a47da78751843.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F22%2F195105_48c2a33b357ba91c701a47da78751843.png&h=3c7406c9&s={SIZE}\" /> 鍾意就上喇"},{"pid":"ae53220ba73702bebefca650ce5325b5de43afe8","tid":537070,"uid":96486,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"484d339602a1862cbbfa847a40f2d687f7f2adc0","tid":537070,"uid":12690,"like":0,"dislike":0,